Type: Package
Package: parkR
Title: Possibly Useful Functions From Simon Parker
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2023-09-30
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Simon", family = "Parker",
           email = "simon.parker@lshtm.ac.uk",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-8214-4496"))
Description: A set of personally useful functions for R, mostly concerning
    report generation with `rmarkdown` and `bookdown`. Incorporates
    `usethis`-like helper functions for generating boilerplate projects, some
    string formatting functions, and a CSL file downloader.
